Package: ContinualMonitor
Type: Package
Title: Functions in this package help decide stopping rules in Phase 1 and Phase 2 clinical trials
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Wei Wei
Maintainer: Wei Wei<wei.wei@yale.edu>
Description: The package includes 4 functions that  (1) efficacy stop ,(2) futility stop ,(3) efficacy +futility stop ,(4) efficacy+futility+toxicity.
